The official Instagram for #HayDay

node.text: We have added new time-limited diamond packages to the shop! 🤩 Each one come with a special exclusive decoration!! What better opportunity than now to stock up on diamonds! But be quick, these packages are only available for a short amount of time! ⏰ #HayDay #DiamondPacks

node.text:
Which TV Show are you currently watching? Tom is a fan of "The Flash" but Angus only watches pirate shows 👀📺 
How about you?

#TVshows #favorite

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hay Day on July 23, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, food, drink and text that says 'HAY DAY KITCHEN PEANUT BUTTER MİLKSHAKE!'.

node.text:
[Link in Bio] What better way to enjoy a hot Summer’s day than with a milkshake!
In this episode, we’re making Hay Day’s Peanut Butter Milkshake!

We’ve prepared an easy recipe and a video, so you can follow along step-by-step.

Go ahead, give it a try! And, make sure to share your Milkshakes using the hashtag #haydaykitchen

node.text:
[Link in Bio] We’re making Summer Rolls! 
A perfect and fresh, veggie-packed meal best enjoyed on hot Summer days!

We’ve prepared an easy recipe and a video, so you can follow along step-by-step.

Go ahead, give it a try!

#haydaykitchen

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hay Day on July 01, 2021. May be a cartoon of text.

node.text:
Farm Pass Season 8 has just started! We hope you all have a lot of fun! 🤩

Available this season:

New exclusive hat: Sand Cowboy Hat for your animals to wear!
Special Decoration #1: Hammock!
Special Decoration #2: Fitting Room!
Free Farm Pass perk: Extra Boat Help!
Free Decoration: Fish Fence!

Head over to your farm, tap on the new Baby Chick House- next to your neighborhood house,- and participate to receive all the great rewards! #FarmPass

node.text:
A new Valley Season has started with a new exclusive decoration as the main reward!

🚨IMPORTANT 🚨We are working hard to fix the Android issues, We're preparing an optional update to resolve this to make sure everyone can play again! We're waiting for the update to be cleared and approved (this can take some time) . We apologize and thank you for the patience!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hay Day on June 28, 2021. May be a cartoon of 2 people and text that says 'HAY DAY M 25 Maggie Special!'.

node.text: Starting today, Maggie has some special birthday offers for you! Now’s a great time to give a new look to your house, truck and roadside shop!
